787
00:47:12.864 --> 00:47:16.664
despite extensive profiling at the exome and RNA levels.

788
00:47:16.724 --> 00:47:20.364
There was, however, loss of heterozygosity of BRCA2

789
00:47:20.424 --> 00:47:23.984
in the tumor. And so this patient responded exceptionally well to

790
00:47:24.024 --> 00:47:27.924
platinum-based chemotherapy followed by targeted therapy with a PARP inhibitor.

791
00:47:28.544 --> 00:47:31.424
She was diagnosed with stage four disease over six years ago.

792
00:47:32.004 --> 00:47:35.864
Still alive today, and the progression points that she had

793
00:47:35.924 --> 00:47:39.534
included multiple CNS lesions and leptomeningeal spread.

794
00:47:39.544 --> 00:47:43.184
But this disease was responsive to chemotherapy for almost four years,

795
00:47:43.804 --> 00:47:46.164
and then a PARP inhibitor for 16 months after that.

796
00:47:47.044 --> 00:47:48.024
And these included really

797
00:47:49.044 --> 00:47:52.784
durable responses of several years with regard to the CNS

798
00:47:53.244 --> 00:47:54.664
and leptomeningeal lesions.

799
00:47:56.944 --> 00:48:00.524
