00:48:29.284 --> 00:48:30.644
and some others that are listed there.

809
00:48:31.724 --> 00:48:35.594
And then cohort two are people with either a personal or

810
00:48:35.764 --> 00:48:37.764
family history of lung cancer who

811
00:48:38.784 --> 00:48:42.704
carry or have relatives who carry pathogenic germline mutations in

