815
00:48:53.784 --> 00:48:57.484
three are those with no known mutations but strong family histories of lung

816
00:48:57.524 --> 00:49:00.964
cancer, and they do not necessarily need to have a history of lung

817
00:49:01.024 --> 00:49:01.924
cancer

