841
00:50:27.336 --> 00:50:30.116
Since then, there have been additional families that have been reported to have

842
00:50:30.156 --> 00:50:33.516
this mutation, another germline EGFR variance.

843
00:50:34.156 --> 00:50:37.916
And what's unique about T790M is that it's actually a well-known

844
00:50:37.956 --> 00:50:41.916
